ang\";s:0:\"\";}}s:11:\"description\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:1019:\"<p>Emails are one of the most rewarding channels in online business, that’s no secret.</p>\r\n<p>\r\nAlmost the entirety of worldwide online market owners state that a big part of their income comes from their mailing list, since <strong>any email sent is a good opportunity to obtain new sales.</strong>\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\nA simple email sent in the right time could bring customers to make a second purchase, a purchase you are currently wasting for each succesful order you receive, and that might be worth hundreds of dollars.\r\n</p>\r\n<p>Imagine if you could send an upsell email to customers who added a specific product to their cart and completed the order. Can you see the opportunity?\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\nSay your customers purchase a set of dishes and the plugin automatically offers them a set of cutlery to go with it, maybe with a small discount used to incentivate the bundled purchase.\r\nWouldn’t that be great?\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\nAnd what if you could send an email based on the category in which purchased product belongs?</p>\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}}s:32:\"http://purl.org/dc/elements/1.1/\";a:1:{s:7:\"creator\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:11:\"Samantha P.\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}}s:40:\"http://purl.org/rss/1.0/modules/content/\";a:1:{s:7:\"encoded\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:1039:\"	<div class=\"row \">\n			<div class=\"cols col-sm-9 \">\n		\r\n<h3>Integrate all of the features of Active Campaign to your shop in less than 30 seconds.</h3>\r\n<p>Our new plugin is made to give WooCommerce all the features of this amazing service taking full advantage of its potential, but with keeping an eye on the ecommerce side.</p>\r\n<p>\r\nThanks to <strong>YITH WooCommerce Active Campaign</strong> you may also create custom forms in just a few instants, assign specific tags, send emails as soon as a purchase treshold is reached and so on&#8230;\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\nWe have also implemented a very important feature that allows you to <strong>segment your user base according to the information entered during the checkout</strong>, for instance you could enter all of the inhabitants of a specific town in a specific list, in order to start a flow of automatic emails containing information and/or promotions didicated to a specific portion of your users\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\nDo you see how many opportunities you are missing?\r\n</p>\r\n	</div>\n	\r\n	</div>\n	\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}}s:36:\"http://wellformedweb.org/CommentAPI/\";a:1:{s:10:\"commentRss\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:74:\"https://yithemes.com/themes/plugins/yith-woocommerce-active-campaign/feed/\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}}s:38:\"http://purl.org/rss/1.0/modules/slash/\";a:1:{s:8:\"comments\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:1:\"0\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}}}}i:1;a:6:{s:4:\"data\";s:39:\"\n		\n		\n		\n		\n		\n		\n		\n		\n				\n			\n		\n		\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";s:5:\"child\";a:5:{s:0:\"\";a:6:{s:5:\"title\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:33:\"YITH WooCommerce Customer History\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}s:4:\"link\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:70:\"https://yithemes.com/themes/plugins/yith-woocommerce-customer-history/\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}s:8:\"comments\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:79:\"https://yithemes.com/themes/plugins/yith-woocommerce-customer-history/#comments\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}s:7:\"pubDate\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:31:\"Tue, 31 May 2016 08:06:00 +0000\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}s:4:\"guid\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:48:\"https://yithemes.com/?post_type=product&p=792579\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:1:{s:0:\"\";a:1:{s:11:\"isPermaLink\";s:5:\"false\";}}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}s:11:\"description\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:578:\"<p>Numbers are very important in business!</p>\r\n<p>\r\nWhich is why behind every major store you will find professionals examining all sorts of data.<br>\r\nTheir objective is to find working solutions aimed at optimizing the overall income.\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\nAlmost 100% of e-commerce stores use analytics in order to understand customers’ behaviour, but none of these tools goes the extra mile, none of these tools analyzes the data from John Doe, your best customer.\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\nAnd you need to know what John Doe does, not just any customers who just stumbled into your website.</p>\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}}s:32:\"http://purl.org/dc/elements/1.1/\";a:1:{s:7:\"creator\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:11:\"Samantha P.\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}}s:40:\"http://purl.org/rss/1.0/modules/content/\";a:1:{s:7:\"encoded\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:8279:\"	<div class=\"row \">\n			<div class=\"cols col-sm-9 \">\n		\r\n<h3>Gather specific information about the pages visited by your customers and improve the chance of them performing another purchase.</h3>\r\n<p>\r\nWould you like to know what Mr. John Doe does while browsing your store pages?\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\nYou would be surprised to know that he looks at a very specific product several times without purchasing it.\r\n<br>\r\nSure, it would be easy to contact him offering him a targeted discount. A custom offer on a specific product would almost immediately turn into a new purchase.\r\n</p>\r\n<p> \r\nSo here is your occasion, we just developed <strong>YITH WooCommerce Customer History</strong>, the plugin that will allows you to see which are the pages each one of your customer actually visits while browsing your store.\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\nThis plugin also allows you to monitor their average purchase value and the latest purchases they made through a handy customer chart.\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\nDeal with the market safely and surely and increase the average value of each customer in a simple and painstaking way.\r\n</p>\r\n	</div>\n	\r\n	<div class=\"cols col-sm-3 \">\n		\n<div class=\"general-features\">\n\n		<h3 class=\"quick-info-title\">Quick info</h3>\n\n<div class=\"quick-info\">\n\n    <table class=\"info \">\n                    <tr>\n                <th>Requires:</th>\n                <td>WordPress 4.0 or higher</td>\n            </tr>\n                            <tr>\n                <th>Compatible up to:</th>\n                <td>WordPress 4.5.x</td>\n            </tr>\n                            <tr>\n                <th>Requires:</th>\n                <td>WooCommerce 2.4.0 or higher</td>\n            </tr>\n                            <tr>\n                <th>Compatible up to:</th>\n                <td>WooCommerce 2.6.x</td>\n            </tr>\n                            <tr>\n                <th>Minimum PHP version:</th>\n                <td>5.4</td>\n            </tr>\n                            <tr>\n                <th>Version:</th>\n                <td>1.0.1</td>\n            </tr>\n                            <tr>\n                <th>Released:</th>\n                <td>2016-06-08</td>\n            </tr>\n                            <tr>\n                <th>100% WPML Compatible:</th>\n                <td>yes</td>\n            </tr>\n                <tr>\n            <th>Translation ready:</th>\n            <td>yes</td>\n        </tr>\n                <tr>\n            <th>Support to:</th>\n            <td>\n                <ul class=\"list-unstyled\">\n                    <li>\n                        All YITH plugins                    </li>\n                    <li>All YITH themes</li>\n                    \n                </ul>\n            </td>\n        </tr>\n    </table>\n\n</div>\n\n<div class=\"quick-info-actions\">\n    <a class=\"btn-sm btn-flat-green\" href=\"//yithemes.com/docs-plugins/yith-woocommerce-customer-history/\"\n       title=\"View documentation\"\n       target=\"_blank\">View documentation</a>\n    <a class=\"btn-sm btn-flat-green\" href=\"#\" title=\"View changelog\"\n       data-toggle=\"modal\" data-target=\"#changelog\">View changelog</a>\n</div>\n\n    <div class=\"modal fade\" id=\"changelog\" tabindex=\"-1\" role=\"dialog\" aria-labelledby=\"changelogLabel\" aria-hidden=\"true\">\n        <div class=\"modal-dialog\">\n            <div class=\"modal-content\">\n                <div class=\"modal-body\">\n                    <button type=\"button\" class=\"close\" data-dismiss=\"modal\" aria-label=\"Close\"><span\n                            aria-hidden=\"true\">&times;</span></button>\n                    \n\n<h4>Version 1.0.1 - Released: Jun 08, 2016</h4>\n<ul>\n    <li>Added: YITH WooCommerce Multi Vendor support</li>\n	<li>Added: WooCommerce 2.6.x support</li>\n</ul>\n<h4>Version 1.0.0 - Released: May 31, 2016</h4>\n<ul>\n    <li>Initial Release</li>\n</ul>\n\n                    </div>\n            </div>\n        </div>\n    </div>\n\n\n</div>\n\n	</div>\n		</div>\n	\r\n<h2 style=\"text-align: center;\">WITH <span class=\"green\">THIS PLUGIN</span> YOU CAN:</h2>\r\n	<div class=\"row border\">\n		\r\n	<div class=\"cols col-sm-6 \">\n		\n	<div class=\"image_title\">\n					<h2>\n				Have an overview about the users			</h2>\n		\n					<h3>\n				Discovering who made more purchases on your site and the average price for each order			</h3>\n			<div class=\"image_title_content\">\n							</div>\n			</div>\n\n		<div class=\"image-from-id\">\n		<img width=\"600\" height=\"551\" class=\"attachment-full size-full\" alt=\"Customers list\" sizes=\"(max-width: 600px) 100vw, 600px\" data-original=\"https://yithemes.com/wp-content/uploads/2016/05/01-9.jpg\" data-original-set=\"https://yithemes.com/wp-content/uploads/2016/05/01-9.jpg 600w, https://yithemes.com/wp-content/uploads/2016/05/01-9-300x276.jpg 300w, https://yithemes.com/wp-content/uploads/2016/05/01-9-382x351.jpg 382w, https://yithemes.com/wp-content/uploads/2016/05/01-9-149x137.jpg 149w\" />	</div>\n		</div>\n		<div class=\"cols col-sm-6 border\">\n		\n	<div class=\"image_title\">\n					<h2>\n				Analyze the users’ behavior			</h2>\n		\n					<h3>\n				Concerning the pages that has been visited and all the actions before purchasing in order to improve your marketing strategies			</h3>\n			<div class=\"image_title_content\">\n							</div>\n			</div>\n\n		<div class=\"image-from-id\">\n		<img width=\"600\" height=\"551\" class=\"attachment-full size-full\" alt=\"Sessions history\" sizes=\"(max-width: 600px) 100vw, 600px\" data-original=\"https://yithemes.com/wp-content/uploads/2016/05/02-6.jpg\" data-original-set=\"https://yithemes.com/wp-content/uploads/2016/05/02-6.jpg 600w, https://yithemes.com/wp-content/uploads/2016/05/02-6-300x276.jpg 300w, https://yithemes.com/wp-content/uploads/2016/05/02-6-382x351.jpg 382w, https://yithemes.com/wp-content/uploads/2016/05/02-6-149x137.jpg 149w\" />	</div>\n		</div>\n	\r\n	</div>\n	\r\n\r\n	<div class=\"row border\">\n		\r\n	<div class=\"cols col-sm-6 \">\n		\n	<div class=\"image_title\">\n					<h2>\n				Understand your users’ need			</h2>\n		\n					<h3>\n				By acquiring all the search keys they type on your site			</h3>\n			<div class=\"image_title_content\">\n							</div>\n			</div>\n\n		<div class=\"image-from-id\">\n		<img width=\"600\" height=\"571\" class=\"attachment-full size-full\" alt=\"Key words for search content\" sizes=\"(max-width: 600px) 100vw, 600px\" data-original=\"https://yithemes.com/wp-content/uploads/2016/05/03-4.jpg\" data-original-set=\"https://yithemes.com/wp-content/uploads/2016/05/03-4.jpg 600w, https://yithemes.com/wp-content/uploads/2016/05/03-4-300x286.jpg 300w, https://yithemes.com/wp-content/uploads/2016/05/03-4-382x364.jpg 382w, https://yithemes.com/wp-content/uploads/2016/05/03-4-144x137.jpg 144w\" />	</div>\n		</div>\n		<div class=\"cols col-sm-6 border\">\n		\n	<div class=\"image_title\">\n					<h2>\n				Contact the users in an easy way			</h2>\n		\n					<h3>\n				By completing the email sending form directly from your administration area			</h3>\n			<div class=\"image_title_content\">\n							</div>\n			</div>\n\n		<div class=\"image-from-id\">\n		<img width=\"600\" height=\"571\" class=\"attachment-full size-full\" alt=\"Email settings\" sizes=\"(max-width: 600px) 100vw, 600px\" data-original=\"https://yithemes.com/wp-content/uploads/2016/05/04-4.jpg\" data-original-set=\"https://yithemes.com/wp-content/uploads/2016/05/04-4.jpg 600w, https://yithemes.com/wp-content/uploads/2016/05/04-4-300x286.jpg 300w, https://yithemes.com/wp-content/uploads/2016/05/04-4-382x364.jpg 382w, https://yithemes.com/wp-content/uploads/2016/05/04-4-144x137.jpg 144w\" />	</div>\n		</div>\n	\r\n	</div>\n	\r\n\r\n	<div class=\"row \">\n		\r\n	<div class=\"cols col-sm-12 \">\n		\n	<div class=\"image_title\">\n					<h2>\n				Filter the information by user			</h2>\n		\n					<h3>\n				By having access to the information details related to him/her			</h3>\n			<div class=\"image_title_content\">\n							</div>\n			</div>\n\n		<div class=\"image-from-id\">\n		<img width=\"745\" height=\"858\" class=\"attachment-full size-full\" alt=\"Customer details\" sizes=\"(max-width: 745px) 100vw, 745px\" data-original=\"https://yithemes.com/wp-content/uploads/2016/05/05-3.jpg\" data-original-set=\"https://yithemes.com/wp-content/uploads/2016/05/05-3.jpg 745w, https://yithemes.com/wp-content/uploads/2016/05/05-3-260x300.jpg 260w, https://yithemes.com/wp-content/uploads/2016/05/05-3-382x440.jpg 382w, https://yithemes.com/wp-content/uploads/2016/05/05-3-119x137.jpg 119w\" />	</div>\n		</div>\n	\r\n	</div>\n	\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}}s:36:\"http://wellformedweb.org/CommentAPI/\";a:1:{s:10:\"commentRss\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:75:\"https://yithemes.com/themes/plugins/yith-woocommerce-customer-history/feed/\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}}s:38:\"http://purl.org/rss/1.0/modules/slash/\";a:1:{s:8:\"comments\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:1:\"4\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}}}}i:2;a:6:{s:4:\"data\";s:39:\"\n		\n		\n		\n		\n		\n		\n		\n		\n				\n			\n		\n		\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";s:5:\"child\";a:5:{s:0:\"\";a:6:{s:5:\"title\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:34:\"YITH WooCommerce Sms Notifications\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}s:4:\"link\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:71:\"https://yithemes.com/themes/plugins/yith-woocommerce-sms-notifications/\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}s:8:\"comments\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:80:\"https://yithemes.com/themes/plugins/yith-woocommerce-sms-notifications/#comments\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}s:7:\"pubDate\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:31:\"Thu, 26 May 2016 12:46:02 +0000\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}s:4:\"guid\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:48:\"https://yithemes.com/?post_type=product&p=791881\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:1:{s:0:\"\";a:1:{s:11:\"isPermaLink\";s:5:\"false\";}}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}s:11:\"description\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:555:\"<p>Have you ever felt like you are part of a family, while purchasing online?</p>\r\n<p>\r\nImagine if after purchasing your favorite product you would receive a custom text message right away, including personal thanks and the information that your purchase has been successful, you know what would happen?\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\nA careful touch will greatly increase customers’ trust towards the company they have chosen to purchase from! And the direct consequence of this is that they will feel pampered and cared for.\r\n</p>\r\n\r\nAll thanks to a simple text message.\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}}s:32:\"http://purl.org/dc/elements/1.1/\";a:1:{s:7:\"creator\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:11:\"Samantha P.\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}}s:40:\"http://purl.org/rss/1.0/modules/content/\";a:1:{s:7:\"encoded\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:12583:\"	<div class=\"row \">\n			<div class=\"cols col-sm-9 \">\n		\r\n<h3>Keep your customers loyal to your store as if you have always known them</h3>\r\n<p>Companies that send text messages to their customers following their purchases or to inform them about any possible issue are often recognized as trustworthy ones.<br>\r\nThink about it: your bank sends you text message notifications when you perform a bank transaction, big clothing stores send their customers text messages as well, what about you?\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\nThanks to our <strong>YITH WooCommerce SMS Notification</strong> you can start sending custom text messages to your customers right away, informing them of any change in the status of the order they placed.\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\nIn order to deliver these text messages, several different gateways are used, such as Twilio and Clockworks and if you wish, you will be able to receive them as well.\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\nIn case you need to be notified via SMS for each processed purchase and any order gone wrong in your store, you will be able to do this in a few clicks and you will have your whole sales under control.\r\n</p>\r\n	</div>\n	\r\n	<div class=\"cols col-sm-3 \">\n		\n<div class=\"general-features\">\n\n		<h3 class=\"quick-info-title\">Quick info</h3>\n\n<div class=\"quick-info\">\n\n    <table class=\"info \">\n                    <tr>\n                <th>Requires:</th>\n                <td>WordPress 4.0 or higher</td>\n            </tr>\n                            <tr>\n                <th>Compatible up to:</th>\n                <td>WordPress 4.5.x</td>\n            </tr>\n                            <tr>\n                <th>Requires:</th>\n                <td>WooCommerce 2.4.0 or higher</td>\n            </tr>\n                            <tr>\n                <th>Compatible up to:</th>\n                <td>WooCommerce 2.6.x</td>\n            </tr>\n                            <tr>\n                <th>Minimum PHP version:</th>\n                <td>5.4</td>\n            </tr>\n                            <tr>\n                <th>Version:</th>\n                <td>1.0.0</td>\n            </tr>\n                            <tr>\n                <th>Released:</th>\n                <td>2016-05-26</td>\n            </tr>\n                            <tr>\n                <th>100% WPML Compatible:</th>\n                <td>yes</td>\n            </tr>\n                <tr>\n            <th>Translation ready:</th>\n            <td>yes</td>\n        </tr>\n                <tr>\n            <th>Support to:</th>\n            <td>\n                <ul class=\"list-unstyled\">\n                    <li>\n                        All YITH plugins                    </li>\n                    <li>All YITH themes</li>\n                    \n                </ul>\n            </td>\n        </tr>\n    </table>\n\n</div>\n\n<div class=\"quick-info-actions\">\n    <a class=\"btn-sm btn-flat-green\" href=\"//yithemes.com/docs-plugins/yith-woocommerce-sms-notifications/\"\n       title=\"View documentation\"\n       target=\"_blank\">View documentation</a>\n    <a class=\"btn-sm btn-flat-green\" href=\"#\" title=\"View changelog\"\n       data-toggle=\"modal\" data-target=\"#changelog\">View changelog</a>\n</div>\n\n    <div class=\"modal fade\" id=\"changelog\" tabindex=\"-1\" role=\"dialog\" aria-labelledby=\"changelogLabel\" aria-hidden=\"true\">\n        <div class=\"modal-dialog\">\n            <div class=\"modal-content\">\n                <div class=\"modal-body\">\n                    <button type=\"button\" class=\"close\" data-dismiss=\"modal\" aria-label=\"Close\"><span\n                            aria-hidden=\"true\">&times;</span></button>\n                    \n\n<h4>Version 1.0.0 - Released on May 26, 2016</h4>\n<ul>\n    <li>Initial Release</li>\n</ul>\n\n                    </div>\n            </div>\n        </div>\n    </div>\n\n\n</div>\n\n	</div>\n		</div>\n	\r\n<h2 style=\"text-align: center;\">WITH <span class=\"green\">THIS PLUGIN</span> YOU CAN:</h2>\r\n	<div class=\"row border\">\n		\r\n	<div class=\"cols col-sm-6 \">\n		\n	<div class=\"image_title\">\n					<h2>\n				Send SMS notifications			</h2>\n		\n					<h3>\n				By choosing the best service among Twilio, Clockwork and Agile Telecom			</h3>\n			<div class=\"image_title_content\">\n							</div>\n			</div>\n\n		<div class=\"image-from-id\">\n		<img width=\"600\" height=\"583\" class=\"attachment-full size-full\" alt=\"Sms service enabled\" sizes=\"(max-width: 600px) 100vw, 600px\" data-original=\"https://yithemes.com/wp-content/uploads/2016/05/01-4.jpg\" data-original-set=\"https://yithemes.com/wp-content/uploads/2016/05/01-4.jpg 600w, https://yithemes.com/wp-content/uploads/2016/05/01-4-300x292.jpg 300w, https://yithemes.com/wp-content/uploads/2016/05/01-4-382x371.jpg 382w, https://yithemes.com/wp-content/uploads/2016/05/01-4-141x137.jpg 141w\" />	</div>\n		</div>\n		<div class=\"cols col-sm-6 border\">\n		\n	<div class=\"image_title\">\n					<h2>\n				Change sender’s configuration			</h2>\n		\n					<h3>\n				By inserting fictitious name and number			</h3>\n			<div class=\"image_title_content\">\n							</div>\n			</div>\n\n		<div class=\"image-from-id\">\n		<img width=\"600\" height=\"583\" class=\"attachment-full size-full\" alt=\"Sender&#039;s configuration\" sizes=\"(max-width: 600px) 100vw, 600px\" data-original=\"https://yithemes.com/wp-content/uploads/2016/05/02-3.jpg\" data-original-set=\"https://yithemes.com/wp-content/uploads/2016/05/02-3.jpg 600w, https://yithemes.com/wp-content/uploads/2016/05/02-3-300x292.jpg 300w, https://yithemes.com/wp-content/uploads/2016/05/02-3-382x371.jpg 382w, https://yithemes.com/wp-content/uploads/2016/05/02-3-141x137.jpg 141w\" />	</div>\n		</div>\n	\r\n	</div>\n	\r\n\r\n	<div class=\"row border\">\n		\r\n	<div class=\"cols col-sm-6 \">\n		\n	<div class=\"image_title\">\n					<h2>\n				Notify the order status			</h2>\n		\n					<h3>\n				Choose for which status you want to enable the SMS notification sending and the related recipients			</h3>\n			<div class=\"image_title_content\">\n							</div>\n			</div>\n\n		<div class=\"image-from-id\">\n		<img width=\"600\" height=\"681\" class=\"attachment-full size-full\" alt=\"Order status changed\" sizes=\"(max-width: 600px) 100vw, 600px\" data-original=\"https://yithemes.com/wp-content/uploads/2016/05/03-2.jpg\" data-original-set=\"https://yithemes.com/wp-content/uploads/2016/05/03-2.jpg 600w, https://yithemes.com/wp-content/uploads/2016/05/03-2-264x300.jpg 264w, https://yithemes.com/wp-content/uploads/2016/05/03-2-382x434.jpg 382w, https://yithemes.com/wp-content/uploads/2016/05/03-2-121x137.jpg 121w\" />	</div>\n		</div>\n		<div class=\"cols col-sm-6 border\">\n		\n	<div class=\"image_title\">\n					<h2>\n				Enable the service for all users			</h2>\n		\n					<h3>\n				Or only for those who request it during the checkout			</h3>\n			<div class=\"image_title_content\">\n							</div>\n			</div>\n\n		<div class=\"image-from-id\">\n		<img width=\"600\" height=\"681\" class=\"attachment-full size-full\" alt=\"Send sms notifications to customer\" sizes=\"(max-width: 600px) 100vw, 600px\" data-original=\"https://yithemes.com/wp-content/uploads/2016/05/04-2.jpg\" data-original-set=\"https://yithemes.com/wp-content/uploads/2016/05/04-2.jpg 600w, https://yithemes.com/wp-content/uploads/2016/05/04-2-264x300.jpg 264w, https://yithemes.com/wp-content/uploads/2016/05/04-2-382x434.jpg 382w, https://yithemes.com/wp-content/uploads/2016/05/04-2-121x137.jpg 121w\" />	</div>\n		</div>\n	\r\n	</div>\n	\r\n\r\n	<div class=\"row border\">\n		\r\n	<div class=\"cols col-sm-6 \">\n		\n	<div class=\"image_title\">\n					<h2>\n				Send admin notifications to other people			</h2>\n		\n					<h3>\n				By inserting, for example, also the shop manager’s number			</h3>\n			<div class=\"image_title_content\">\n							</div>\n			</div>\n\n		<div class=\"image-from-id\">\n		<img width=\"600\" height=\"499\" class=\"attachment-full size-full\" alt=\"Admin phone\" sizes=\"(max-width: 600px) 100vw, 600px\" data-original=\"https://yithemes.com/wp-content/uploads/2016/05/05-2.jpg\" data-original-set=\"https://yithemes.com/wp-content/uploads/2016/05/05-2.jpg 600w, https://yithemes.com/wp-content/uploads/2016/05/05-2-300x250.jpg 300w, https://yithemes.com/wp-content/uploads/2016/05/05-2-382x318.jpg 382w, https://yithemes.com/wp-content/uploads/2016/05/05-2-165x137.jpg 165w\" />	</div>\n		</div>\n		<div class=\"cols col-sm-6 border\">\n		\n	<div class=\"image_title\">\n					<h2>\n				Optimize the 160 characters available for each SMS			</h2>\n		\n					<h3>\n				By taking advantage of Google or Bitly services to reduce the URL length that you want to include in the message			</h3>\n			<div class=\"image_title_content\">\n							</div>\n			</div>\n\n		<div class=\"image-from-id\">\n		<img width=\"600\" height=\"499\" class=\"attachment-full size-full\" alt=\"Url shortening settings\" sizes=\"(max-width: 600px) 100vw, 600px\" data-original=\"https://yithemes.com/wp-content/uploads/2016/05/06-1.jpg\" data-original-set=\"https://yithemes.com/wp-content/uploads/2016/05/06-1.jpg 600w, https://yithemes.com/wp-content/uploads/2016/05/06-1-300x250.jpg 300w, https://yithemes.com/wp-content/uploads/2016/05/06-1-382x318.jpg 382w, https://yithemes.com/wp-content/uploads/2016/05/06-1-165x137.jpg 165w\" />	</div>\n		</div>\n	\r\n	</div>\n	\r\n\r\n	<div class=\"row border\">\n		\r\n	<div class=\"cols col-sm-6 \">\n		\n	<div class=\"image_title\">\n					<h2>\n				Reduce the distance with your customers			</h2>\n		\n					<h3>\n				By sending the SMS manually when you need to ask for further information about their orders			</h3>\n			<div class=\"image_title_content\">\n							</div>\n			</div>\n\n		<div class=\"image-from-id\">\n		<img width=\"600\" height=\"587\" class=\"attachment-full size-full\" alt=\"Send manually sms to customer\" sizes=\"(max-width: 600px) 100vw, 600px\" data-original=\"https://yithemes.com/wp-content/uploads/2016/05/07-1.jpg\" data-original-set=\"https://yithemes.com/wp-content/uploads/2016/05/07-1.jpg 600w, https://yithemes.com/wp-content/uploads/2016/05/07-1-65x65.jpg 65w, https://yithemes.com/wp-content/uploads/2016/05/07-1-300x294.jpg 300w, https://yithemes.com/wp-content/uploads/2016/05/07-1-382x374.jpg 382w, https://yithemes.com/wp-content/uploads/2016/05/07-1-140x137.jpg 140w\" />	</div>\n		</div>\n		<div class=\"cols col-sm-6 border\">\n		\n	<div class=\"image_title\">\n					<h2>\n				Customize the text of your automatic messages			</h2>\n		\n					<h3>\n				By recovering the order information in a dynamic way			</h3>\n			<div class=\"image_title_content\">\n							</div>\n			</div>\n\n		<div class=\"image-from-id\">\n		<img width=\"600\" height=\"587\" class=\"attachment-full size-full\" alt=\"Sms settings\" sizes=\"(max-width: 600px) 100vw, 600px\" data-original=\"https://yithemes.com/wp-content/uploads/2016/05/08-1.jpg\" data-original-set=\"https://yithemes.com/wp-content/uploads/2016/05/08-1.jpg 600w, https://yithemes.com/wp-content/uploads/2016/05/08-1-65x65.jpg 65w, https://yithemes.com/wp-content/uploads/2016/05/08-1-300x294.jpg 300w, https://yithemes.com/wp-content/uploads/2016/05/08-1-382x374.jpg 382w, https://yithemes.com/wp-content/uploads/2016/05/08-1-140x137.jpg 140w\" />	</div>\n		</div>\n	\r\n	</div>\n	\r\n\r\n	<div class=\"row \">\n		\r\n	<div class=\"cols col-sm-6 \">\n		\n	<div class=\"image_title\">\n					<h2>\n				Verify the correct functioning of the service			</h2>\n		\n					<h3>\n				By sending a test message to the specified number			</h3>\n			<div class=\"image_title_content\">\n							</div>\n			</div>\n\n		<div class=\"image-from-id\">\n		<img width=\"600\" height=\"837\" class=\"attachment-full size-full\" alt=\"Send test sms\" sizes=\"(max-width: 600px) 100vw, 600px\" data-original=\"https://yithemes.com/wp-content/uploads/2016/05/09.jpg\" data-original-set=\"https://yithemes.com/wp-content/uploads/2016/05/09.jpg 600w, https://yithemes.com/wp-content/uploads/2016/05/09-215x300.jpg 215w, https://yithemes.com/wp-content/uploads/2016/05/09-382x533.jpg 382w, https://yithemes.com/wp-content/uploads/2016/05/09-98x137.jpg 98w\" />	</div>\n		</div>\n		<div class=\"cols col-sm-6 border\">\n		\n	<div class=\"image_title\">\n					<h2>\n				Enable SMS sending also for the status of custom orders			</h2>\n		\n					<h3>\n				By taking advantage of the compatibility with YITH WooCommerce Custom Order Status			</h3>\n			<div class=\"image_title_content\">\n							</div>\n			</div>\n\n		<div class=\"image-from-id\">\n		<img width=\"600\" height=\"837\" class=\"attachment-full size-full\" alt=\"By taking advantage of the compatibility with YITH WooCommerce Custom Order Status\" sizes=\"(max-width: 600px) 100vw, 600px\" data-original=\"https://yithemes.com/wp-content/uploads/2016/05/10.jpg\" data-original-set=\"https://yithemes.com/wp-content/uploads/2016/05/10.jpg 600w, https://yithemes.com/wp-content/uploads/2016/05/10-215x300.jpg 215w, https://yithemes.com/wp-content/uploads/2016/05/10-382x533.jpg 382w, https://yithemes.com/wp-content/uploads/2016/05/10-98x137.jpg 98w\" />	</div>\n		</div>\n	\r\n	</div>\n	\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}}s:36:\"http://wellformedweb.org/CommentAPI/\";a:1:{s:10:\"commentRss\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:76:\"https://yithemes.com/themes/plugins/yith-woocommerce-sms-notifications/feed/\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}}s:38:\"http://purl.org/rss/1.0/modules/slash/\";a:1:{s:8:\"comments\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:1:\"3\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}}}}i:3;a:6:{s:4:\"data\";s:39:\"\n		\n		\n		\n		\n		\n		\n		\n		\n				\n			\n		\n		\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";s:5:\"child\";a:5:{s:0:\"\";a:6:{s:5:\"title\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:41:\"YITH WooCommerce Paypal Adaptive payments\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}s:4:\"link\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:78:\"https://yithemes.com/themes/plugins/yith-woocommerce-paypal-adaptive-payments/\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}s:8:\"comments\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:86:\"https://yithemes.com/themes/plugins/yith-woocommerce-paypal-adaptive-payments/#respond\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}s:7:\"pubDate\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:31:\"Wed, 25 May 2016 12:17:28 +0000\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}s:4:\"guid\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:48:\"https://yithemes.com/?post_type=product&p=793902\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:1:{s:0:\"\";a:1:{s:11:\"isPermaLink\";s:5:\"false\";}}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}s:11:\"description\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:625:\"<p>Imagine this scenario:<br>\r\nYou are spending time with a colleague of yours while you get the idea of selling online a product you are going to work together at, after the initial moment of euphoria, then a list of questions wil arise such as: How will we divide the income? When are we going to get paid? Who is going to keep track of the payments?\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\nUnfortunately in most cases, these questions are not easily answered and can be cause to a lot of frustration.\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\nThis could be the case of a video course, a music file or any kind of creative work you decided to share 50% of your income with.\r\n</p>\r\n\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}}s:32:\"http://purl.org/dc/elements/1.1/\";a:1:{s:7:\"creator\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:11:\"Samantha P.\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}}s:40:\"http://purl.org/rss/1.0/modules/content/\";a:1:{s:7:\"encoded\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:1003:\"	<div class=\"row \">\n			<div class=\"cols col-sm-9 \">\n		\r\n<h3>Sell your products online sharing your earnings with your collaborators or partners</h3>\r\n<p>YITH WOOCOMMERCE PAYPAL ADAPTIVE PAYMENTS allows you to share the payments you receive on your store with all the partners you want, instantly and automatically.</p>\r\n<p>\r\nYou will just have to specify the share of the income and your partner’s PayPal account and our plugin will take care of the rest , using PayPal’s API keys it will let you share the payments of all of your sales andr to receive the money immediately on each respective account.\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\nThis system is great! It will not only allow you to have a potential number of collaborators or partners, but you will also be able to handle them in a quick and easy way.\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\nBesides, thanks to the compatibility with our best seller plugin YITH Multi Vendor you can perform automatic payments to all of your vendors in order to save precious time.\r\n</p>\r\n	</div>\n	\r\n	</div>\n	\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}}s:36:\"http://wellformedweb.org/CommentAPI/\";a:1:{s:10:\"commentRss\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:83:\"https://yithemes.com/themes/plugins/yith-woocommerce-paypal-adaptive-payments/feed/\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}}s:38:\"http://purl.org/rss/1.0/modules/slash/\";a:1:{s:8:\"comments\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:1:\"0\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}}}}i:4;a:6:{s:4:\"data\";s:39:\"\n		\n		\n		\n		\n		\n		\n		\n		\n				\n			\n		\n		\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";s:5:\"child\";a:5:{s:0:\"\";a:6:{s:5:\"title\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:22:\"YITH WooCommerce Ideas\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}s:4:\"link\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:59:\"https://yithemes.com/themes/plugins/yith-woocommerce-ideas/\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}s:8:\"comments\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:67:\"https://yithemes.com/themes/plugins/yith-woocommerce-ideas/#respond\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}s:7:\"pubDate\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:31:\"Wed, 25 May 2016 08:54:42 +0000\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}s:4:\"guid\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:48:\"https://yithemes.com/?post_type=product&p=792970\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:1:{s:0:\"\";a:1:{s:11:\"isPermaLink\";s:5:\"false\";}}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}s:11:\"description\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:660:\"<p>You are one step away from turning the launch of each single product or service into a guaranteed success… and YITH WooCommerce Ideas can help you take this step!</p>\r\n<p>\r\nOne of the most important aspects of any product launch method is to gather <strong>tips and opinions from customers</strong> so that once the product is effectively on sale, you can offer exactly what they are after.\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\nThis is usually obtained using complex <strong>surveys</strong> and <strong>newsletters</strong>, systems which may prove to be ultimately counterproductive… It’s best to use an automated and optimized system thanks to YITH WooCommerce Ideas.\r\n</p>\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}}s:32:\"http://purl.org/dc/elements/1.1/\";a:1:{s:7:\"creator\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:11:\"Samantha P.\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}}s:40:\"http://purl.org/rss/1.0/modules/content/\";a:1:{s:7:\"encoded\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:1517:\"	<div class=\"row \">\n			<div class=\"cols col-sm-9 \">\n		\r\n<h3>If two heads work better than one, then think about a hundred or a thousand heads! Use your customers’ ideas to increase your sales!</h3>\r\n<p>There are many extremely effective <strong>marketing</strong> systems that are no longer being used since they might seem complex to new vendors or because they require more time than we can spare… But today, this is no longer the case!\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\nThis plugin introduces an automated system which will allow your customers to propose their own tips and <strong>ideas</strong> for products, services or projects that are in development (with the possibility of limiting this feature to registred users only or just anybody) and evaluate these proposal so that the strongest, most requested and (consequently) most advantageous ones will be highlighted.\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\nThanks to a handy list of proposed ideas and the chance to use a shortcode to display this function within your website, <strong>YITH WooCommerce Ideas</strong> will grant admins complete control over an automated, optimized and effective system which will allow you to offer products with a much higher selling power than they would normally have.\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\nThis plugin is simply ideal for those who wish to show a project to the public, for creative people who wish to have a feedback on their creations, charity projects or simply anybody who wishes to optimize their products and increase their sales right away!\r\n</p>\r\n	</div>\n	\r\n	</div>\n	\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}}s:36:\"http://wellformedweb.org/CommentAPI/\";a:1:{s:10:\"commentRss\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:64:\"https://yithemes.com/themes/plugins/yith-woocommerce-ideas/feed/\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}}s:38:\"http://purl.org/rss/1.0/modules/slash/\";a:1:{s:8:\"comments\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:1:\"0\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}}}}i:5;a:6:{s:4:\"data\";s:39:\"\n		\n		\n		\n		\n		\n		\n		\n		\n				\n			\n		\n		\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";s:5:\"child\";a:5:{s:0:\"\";a:6:{s:5:\"title\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:24:\"YITH WooCommerce Booking\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}s:4:\"link\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:61:\"https://yithemes.com/themes/plugins/yith-woocommerce-booking/\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}s:8:\"comments\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:69:\"https://yithemes.com/themes/plugins/yith-woocommerce-booking/#respond\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}s:7:\"pubDate\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:31:\"Mon, 23 May 2016 13:45:32 +0000\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}s:4:\"guid\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:48:\"https://yithemes.com/?post_type=product&p=793536\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:1:{s:0:\"\";a:1:{s:11:\"isPermaLink\";s:5:\"false\";}}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}s:11:\"description\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:884:\"<p>Are you tired of losing customers due to a complex and ineffective booking system? Would you like to receive a bigger number of bookings and optimize your ability?\r\nYITH WooCommerce Booking is the plugin you are looking for!<br>\r\nBuilt under direct request by our many customers, YITH WooCommerce Booking integrates a regular <strong>e-commerce store</strong> built using WooCommerce with a simple <strong>booking system</strong> which can be used by both customers and vendors: this is ideal for all of those professionals who cannot base their business on sales alone.\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\nYITH WooCommerce Booking is a plugin developed for <strong>estate agencies</strong> and <strong>travel agencies</strong>, but not just for them! Hairdressers, doctors, business consultants and all of those who can benefit from a booking system for travels, items or dates should try it out!\r\n</p>\r\n\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}}s:32:\"http://purl.org/dc/elements/1.1/\";a:1:{s:7:\"creator\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:11:\"Samantha P.\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}}s:40:\"http://purl.org/rss/1.0/modules/content/\";a:1:{s:7:\"encoded\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:1601:\"	<div class=\"row \">\n			<div class=\"cols col-sm-9 \">\n		\r\n<h3>Boost your sales starting now thanks to an easy and efficient booking system!</h3>\r\n<p>YITH WooCommerce Booking was one of our most requested plugin, which is why we were able to shape it around your needs!</p>\r\n\r\n<p>This plugin allows you to create a dynamic booking system, the price will be processed in real time according to your customers’ requests. This allows you to arrange your <strong>bookings</strong> by date, period or season, number of people involved and much more.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>YITH WooCommerce Booking also allows you to perform targeted searches within your website, using advanced search filters such as data, number of bookings, location and services.<br>\r\nYou will have a clear and effective view of the bookings in your website and have the chance to arrange your requests using a number of filters such as: date, period, checkout date, name, family name and much more! You will also be able to export the bookings in your website in csv, pdf or excel and see the full schedule of your work!\r\n</p>\r\n<p>This plugin also offers many other features that will help you customize and optimize your website, such as a specific way of handling your booking emails, the chance of adding a map and a detailed booking checkout system. <br>\r\n<strong>YITH WooCommerce Booking</strong> is also compatible with many of our other plugins, such as Multi Vendor, Membership, Request a Quote and Role Based Prices, in order for you to be able to create your perfect custom offer for any possible circumstance!\r\n</p>\r\n	</div>\n	\r\n	</div>\n	\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}}s:36:\"http://wellformedweb.org/CommentAPI/\";a:1:{s:10:\"commentRss\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:66:\"https://yithemes.com/themes/plugins/yith-woocommerce-booking/feed/\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}}s:38:\"http://purl.org/rss/1.0/modules/slash/\";a:1:{s:8:\"comments\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:1:\"0\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}}}}i:6;a:6:{s:4:\"data\";s:39:\"\n		\n		\n		\n		\n		\n		\n		\n		\n				\n			\n		\n		\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";s:5:\"child\";a:5:{s:0:\"\";a:6:{s:5:\"title\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:38:\"YITH WooCommerce Barcodes and QR Codes\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}s:4:\"link\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:75:\"https://yithemes.com/themes/plugins/yith-woocommerce-barcodes-and-qr-codes/\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}s:8:\"comments\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:84:\"https://yithemes.com/themes/plugins/yith-woocommerce-barcodes-and-qr-codes/#comments\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}s:7:\"pubDate\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:31:\"Fri, 20 May 2016 09:26:37 +0000\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}s:4:\"guid\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:48:\"https://yithemes.com/?post_type=product&p=788504\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:1:{s:0:\"\";a:1:{s:11:\"isPermaLink\";s:5:\"false\";}}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}s:11:\"description\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:369:\"<strong>When does the state of tension increase? </strong><br>\r\nWhen a received package must be shipped. Even the smallest mistake could cause negative consequences. Tension also increases when the products of your shop must be loaded or unloaded from the stock or when you need to know which items are contained inside an Out For Delivery package.\r\n[spacer size=\"100\"]\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}}s:32:\"http://purl.org/dc/elements/1.1/\";a:1:{s:7:\"creator\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:11:\"Samantha P.\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}}s:40:\"http://purl.org/rss/1.0/modules/content/\";a:1:{s:7:\"encoded\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:10109:\"	<div class=\"row \">\n			<div class=\"cols col-sm-9 \">\n		\r\n<h3>Not everyone knows the best way to avoid these mistakes</h3>\r\n<p>Thanks to the reading of a simple series of numbers generated by the use of bar codes, you can apply some automations to completely remove those annoying mistakes.<br>\r\nAll you need is a <strong>bar code reader</strong> which could be easily used to change an order from “Out For Delivery” status ino “sent” with just one gesture.\r\n</p>\r\n \r\n<p>This is the reason why it is used one billion times a day since 40 years.</p>\r\n \r\n<p><strong>YITH WooCommerce Barcodes and QR Codes</strong> allows you to generate and read bar codes and qr codes. They are automatically generated both on products and on orders. You can combine each reading with a specific action in order to <b>automate and speed your work</b> without mistakes. </p>\r\n	</div>\n	\r\n	<div class=\"cols col-sm-3 \">\n		\n<div class=\"general-features\">\n\n		<h3 class=\"quick-info-title\">Quick info</h3>\n\n<div class=\"quick-info\">\n\n    <table class=\"info \">\n                    <tr>\n                <th>Requires:</th>\n                <td>WordPress 4.0 or higher</td>\n            </tr>\n                            <tr>\n                <th>Compatible up to:</th>\n                <td>WordPress 4.5.x</td>\n            </tr>\n                            <tr>\n                <th>Requires:</th>\n                <td>WooCommerce 2.4.0 or higher</td>\n            </tr>\n                            <tr>\n                <th>Compatible up to:</th>\n                <td>WooCommerce 2.6.x</td>\n            </tr>\n                            <tr>\n                <th>Minimum PHP version:</th>\n                <td>5.4</td>\n            </tr>\n                            <tr>\n                <th>Version:</th>\n                <td>1.0.3</td>\n            </tr>\n                            <tr>\n                <th>Released:</th>\n                <td>2016-06-21</td>\n            </tr>\n                            <tr>\n                <th>100% WPML Compatible:</th>\n                <td>yes</td>\n            </tr>\n                <tr>\n            <th>Translation ready:</th>\n            <td>yes</td>\n        </tr>\n                <tr>\n            <th>Support to:</th>\n            <td>\n                <ul class=\"list-unstyled\">\n                    <li>\n                        All YITH plugins                    </li>\n                    <li>All YITH themes</li>\n                    \n                </ul>\n            </td>\n        </tr>\n    </table>\n\n</div>\n\n<div class=\"quick-info-actions\">\n    <a class=\"btn-sm btn-flat-green\" href=\"//yithemes.com/docs-plugins/yith-woocommerce-barcodes/\"\n       title=\"View documentation\"\n       target=\"_blank\">View documentation</a>\n    <a class=\"btn-sm btn-flat-green\" href=\"#\" title=\"View changelog\"\n       dat